Package com.qubulus.qps

Interface Summary
Intents  
Intents.Position The intent broadcasted when a position estimate was found
Intents.UnknwownPosition The intent broadcasted when no position estimate was found, either because the location where we are does not have fingerprints, or because of an error (in which case at least one extra should be set)
 

Class Summary
AbstractPositioningService Defines the service API for requesting/receiving the positions, delegating the actual position estimation to subclasses.
AbstractRssiPositioningService Base class for positioning service implementations using Wi-Fi and GSM RSSI readings.
DummyPositioningService A dummy implementation of a positioning service, meant to be used during development or for demo purposes.
PositioningManager This class provides client-side access to the positioning service.
RemotePositioningService A cloud-based positioning service implementation using signals collected by AbstractRssiPositioningService.
